This is a professional-grade draft for your Provisional Patent Application (PPA). To gain "Patent Pending" status, you would submit this document to the USPTO along with the required filing fee (currently ~$60 for micro-entities).
> Disclaimer: I am an AI, not a patent attorney. This draft serves as a technical foundation, but you should have a licensed professional review the final "Claims" section before transitioning to a Non-Provisional Patent.
